sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant U as User
    participant FE as Frontend (Browser / Ajax)
    participant API as Backend REST API
    participant CS as Category Filter Service
    participant DB as Database

    U->>FE: Click category filter

    FE->>API: GET /api/products?categoryId=3&page=0&size=12

    API->>CS: filterProducts(categoryId,page,size)

    CS->>DB: SELECT * FROM PRODUCTS\nWHERE category_id=3\nLIMIT page,size
    DB-->>CS: filtered products

    CS-->>API: ProductPage

    API-->>FE: ApiResponse<ProductPage>

    FE-->>U: Refresh product grid